This is not a standalone app, you need to install v3.39 above version (LATEST is recommended) of GO SMS Pro app in order to apply this theme. (Search âGO SMS Proâ to download)2. To apply the theme within GO SMS Pro, download it from Menu->Theme (or Plug-in UI->Theme shop). After downloaded and installed, it will displayed in "My Theme" Tab, click and apply it.3. This is a free theme, just enjoy it.GO Sms Pro theme gosmstheme

reviews.title: Just what I need
reviews.comment: No issues at all, what I wanted was an app that split long messages but also put tags ex.(1/3) at the beginning so the person receiving them would know be able to tell how many messages to expect. This app does that and so much more love the theme options and so many settings. Beyond expectations.
